sequenceDiagram
    participant State
    participant Desc as Descriptor
    participant Read
    participant Write

    Note over State: Cycle 0 - IDLE
    State->>Desc: Request descriptor
    Note over State: Cycle 1 - FETCH_DESC
    Desc-->>State: Descriptor ready
    Note over State: Cycle 2-N - XFER_DATA
    State->>Read: sched_rd_valid (concurrent)
    State->>Write: sched_wr_valid (concurrent)
    Read-->>State: done strobe
    Write-->>State: done strobe
    Note over State: Cycle N+1 - XFER_DATA continues
    Read-->>State: done strobe
    Write-->>State: done strobe
    Note over State: Cycle N+2 - COMPLETE
    Note over State: Cycle N+3 - IDLE
